1. *Postao* je posvećen muzici i nije želeo da radi ništa drugo. (He became devoted to music and didn't want to do anything else.)

2. On je od male dece *postao* poznata ličnost. (He became a well-known person from a young age.)

3. On je *postao* čovek koga su svi poštovali. (He became a man that everyone respected.)

4. Naša deca su *postala* dobra prijatelja. (Our children became good friends.)

5. *Postali* smo prilično bliski u toku godine. (We became quite close over the course of the year.)

6. Njegov život je *postao* toliko različit nakon toga. (His life became so different after that.)

7. *Postao* je veoma uspešan u svojoj profesiji. (He became very successful in his profession.)

8. Oni su *postali* toliko bogati tokom godina. (They became so wealthy over the years.)